{"code":0,"message":"","data":null,"sentence":{"phonemes":[],"text":"I was once a cat. The magician turned me into a poisonous mushroom, letting me drink deeply of nature's rain and dew. As a cat, merely existing in stillness could be interpreted as seduction. But becoming a mushroom has filled my life with laughter.","words":[]}}
